comments: Haaaaaard class! I probably worked harder in this class than almost any other literature/writing-based course. Wow! But it was worth it. Dr. Rodriguez is an interesting guy, and the class actually helped me to finally appreciate poetry. I think he\'s gone from NAU now? Not sure. Too bad, I really enjoyed that class.

This class was very hard. He\'s a good teacher and knows his stuff, but he is a hard grader. I got a low grade for my rough drafts and I followed all the corrections and still got a C. If you really like English and writing take this class, if not take something easier!
One of the most interesting classes I\'ve taken. Challenging but fun. Rodriguez in genuinely interested in what the student have to say, and I could listen to him talk all day!
